        "testimonial_BaC37W": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "title": "",
            "description": "<p>“As a first-time buyer, I was nervous about choosing the right silicone figure, but EternaDoll’s guide made it easy. I customized mine with my favorite hair color and eye shape, and it turned out perfect. It’s soft, well-made, and exactly what I wanted. I couldn’t be happier!”</p>",
